	This Garden Candle Torch from Ashleigh &amp; Burwood is of premium quality and burns for approx 18 hours. It contains a delightful blend of rosemary, citronella and thyme which are an ideal mix to help keep insects at bay. Plant the torch firmly in the ground away from foliage and ideally burn the candle for a maximum of 3 hours at a time. Beautiful for any size of garden giving off a lovely scent and candlelight combined. Perfect for a relaxing evening. Not for indoor use.</p>
